---
// src/pages/sobre.astro
import '../styles/global.css';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Sobre a Comissão | CCF</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-[#FDF8EE] text-[#4A2E15] min-h-screen font-sans flex flex-col relative overflow-x-hidden">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-5 mix-blend-multiply z-0" 
         style="background-image: url('/textura-danca.jpg'); background-size: 600px; background-repeat: repeat;">
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
      <Header />
      
      <section class="relative w-full h-80 md:h-[450px]">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/433/1920/800" alt="Cultura Cearense" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[30%] sepia-[0.2]" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4A2E15]/95 to-[#4A2E15]/40 flex items-center">
          <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full mt-10">
            <span class="text-[#D4A373] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3 block">Institucional</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[#FDF8EE] mb-6 tracking-tight">Sobre a Comissão</h1>
            <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-[#0B5D3F] rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <main class="flex-grow max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 w-full">

        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center mb-24">
          
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-lg text-[#4A2E15]/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#4A2E15] mb-8 tracking-tight leading-tight">A Raiz da Nossa <br class="hidden lg:block"/> História e Trajetória</h2>
            <p>
              Fundada em 1948, a Comissão Cearense de Folclore (CCF) surgiu do anseio de pesquisadores e intelectuais em registrar, proteger e difundir as manifestações culturais de todas as regiões do Ceará.
            </p>
            <p>
              Semelhante a projetos contemporâneos essenciais como o Digital Mundo Miraíra, nós entendemos que a cultura popular não é apenas um registro do passado, mas uma ferramenta viva de educação patrimonial. Trabalhamos para criar um ambiente onde a história dialoga com o presente.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex-1 w-full flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
            <div class="relative w-full max-w-md bg-white p-4 pb-6 border-2 border-[#4A2E15] shadow-[12px_12px_0px_#D4A373] rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
              
              <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-16 h-6 bg-[#FDF8EE] border border-[#D4A373]/30 shadow-sm -rotate-3 z-10 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
              
              <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] border-2 border-[#4A2E15] bg-[#4A2E15] overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/367/800/600" alt="Registro Histórico" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale sepia-[0.35] contrast-125 hover:grayscale-0 hover:sepia-0 transition-all duration-700" />
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-center text-[#4A2E15]/70 font-serif italic text-sm mt-4">
                Acervo documental cearense.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#0B5D3F] border-2 border-[#4A2E15] p-10 md:p-16 text-center text-white shadow-[12px_12px_0px_#4A2E15] mb-24 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-40 h-40 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -translate-y-20 translate-x-20"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full translate-y-16 -translate-x-16"></div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D4A373]">Nossa Missão</h3>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto text-[#FDF8EE]">
            "Atuar na pesquisa, preservação, valorização e difusão do folclore cearense, garantindo que os saberes e fazeres de nossos mestres continuem vivos, pulsantes e acessíveis a toda a sociedade."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          
          <div class="bg-[#FDF8EE] p-8 border-2 border-[#4A2E15] shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#D4A373] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_#0B5D3F] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white border-2 border-[#4A2E15] rounded-none flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:bg-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#4A2E15] mb-3">Pesquisa Extensiva</h4>
            <p class="text-[#4A2E15]/80 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Mapeamento contínuo das manifestações culturais, crenças e ofícios em todo o território estadual.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#FDF8EE] p-8 border-2 border-[#4A2E15] shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#D4A373] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_#0B5D3F] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white border-2 border-[#4A2E15] rounded-none flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:bg-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#4A2E15] mb-3">Educação e Mestres</h4>
            <p class="text-[#4A2E15]/80 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Apoio direto aos grupos de tradição e integração da cultura popular nas ações de educação patrimonial.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#FDF8EE] p-8 border-2 border-[#4A2E15] shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#D4A373] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_#0B5D3F] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white border-2 border-[#4A2E15] rounded-none flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:bg-[#0B5D3F] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#4A2E15] mb-3">Acervo Digital</h4>
            <p class="text-[#4A2E15]/80 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Disponibilização de um banco de dados virtual rico e focado para estudantes e a sociedade civil.</p>
          </div>

        </div>

      </main>

      <Footer />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>